    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR Adventure and walking simulator. Inspired by 90s cartoons. It's a small game that takes about an hour to complete. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're trapped in the middle of the forest, and you must get out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Warm/Cold system. Use fires to keep warm, and plan your next steps carefully. Don't get lost in the fog!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use bow and arrows to build your own path. You choose where to go next!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect keys and magical orbs to unlock doors/gates/chests. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is my first game, I hope you like it!</p>",
